<i>Amy: Mallory's leaving today.</i>

40:44.497 --> 40:46.264
That's impossible!
She would have said something.

40:46.332 --> 40:49.500
Ty: Yeah, I was just talking to her
yesterday, but not about Europe.

40:49.534 --> 40:51.068
It was about Maggie's
and Jake.

40:51.135 --> 40:53.437
Lou: And oh my God, I basically
told her to get out of town

40:53.505 --> 40:55.205
before it's too late.

40:55.240 --> 40:59.042
All she had to do was hit a
couple buttons on her computer

40:59.110 --> 41:02.680
and she was booked on a flight
to Paris, just like that.

41:02.714 --> 41:04.180
What time is she leaving?

41:04.214 --> 41:05.448
Oh, I think she's on her way;

41:05.516 --> 41:07.350
She's probably
at the bus station now.

41:07.385 --> 41:09.218
What happened
to two weeks notice?

41:09.253 --> 41:11.454
<i>Jack: Does it matter, Lou?</i>

41:11.522 --> 41:15.224
Oh hell, I'll wash dishes and
serve tables if you need me to,

41:15.259 --> 41:17.193
just don't make me wear
one of those uniforms.

41:17.227 --> 41:18.595
[Katie moans and passes gas]

41:18.629 --> 41:20.729
Lou: Oh! Honey, you...

41:20.764 --> 41:22.464
You know what, grandpa?
If you really wanna help,

41:22.499 --> 41:24.867
maybe you can handle
bathroom duties.

41:24.901 --> 41:28.637
After all, she was on your watch
when she swallowed the penny.

41:28.705 --> 41:30.205
You should deal
with the consequences.

41:30.273 --> 41:35.810
Jack: Okay, okay. Come on, Katie, you
want to take a ride on a porcelain pony?

41:35.878 --> 41:37.044
Come on.

41:38.013 --> 41:39.313
<i>Amy:</i>
<i>It just doesn't seem fair.</i>

41:39.347 --> 41:40.915
You know, we didn't even get
to say a proper goodbye.

41:40.982 --> 41:42.283
Ty: We gotta do something.

41:42.350 --> 41:44.051
We could send a text.

41:44.119 --> 41:46.487
Amy: Yeah, but that
seems so impersonal.

41:46.522 --> 41:47.655
Hey, you know what?

41:47.723 --> 41:49.123
I think there might be
a better way.

41:50.492 --> 41:54.895
♪

41:54.962 --> 41:57.263
[Shuttle bus rumbles to a stop]

42:02.904 --> 42:07.907
♪ Show me a sign ♪
things will be fine

