<i>bus driver: You getting on?</i>

42:13.780 --> 42:14.947
<i>Okay.</i>

42:14.981 --> 42:20.185
♪ I see the world,
the same one you do ♪

42:20.253 --> 42:25.323
♪ But I want to believe
that we'll make it through ♪

42:25.390 --> 42:26.390
[Toilet flushes]

42:26.459 --> 42:28.626
<i>Jack: That-a girl, you did it!</i>

42:28.694 --> 42:32.430
Good news, everybody,
the penny has... dropped.

42:32.465 --> 42:37.268
♪ I'd like to think
that we're smart enough ♪

42:38.203 --> 42:43.206
♪ To do the right things
no matter how tough ♪

42:44.342 --> 42:47.643
♪ I see the world...

