<i>Bus driver:</i>
<i>Good afternoon, folks,</i>

42:48.980 --> 42:50.280
<i>just wondering</i>
<i>if there's anybody on the bus</i>

42:50.348 --> 42:51.747
<i>named mallory?</i>

42:52.783 --> 42:54.417
<i>If so, you might wanna</i>
<i>take a look</i>

42:54.485 --> 42:55.551
<i>out the right side window.</i>

